Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.berkeley.nlp.lm.util.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends Object
    Basic logging singleton class. The underlying LogInterface instance can be changed to customize logging behaviour by calling setGlobalLogger.

    adampauls
